{"tid":133554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那地產合資破記錄170億投得鴨脷洲地皮    料新樓售價每呎逾3萬","createTime":"2017-02-24T16:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T00:58:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fdbd4cac76f9bf0eb230de0b596033bfbf447e3","tid":133554,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/龍光地產及合景泰富合資以近170億投得鴨脷洲地皮-085116161.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%BE%8D%E5%85%89%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%88%E6%99%AF%E6%B3%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%90%88%E8%B3%87%E4%BB%A5%E8%BF%91170%E5%84%84%E6%8A%95%E5%BE%97%E9%B4%A8%E8%84%B7%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%AE-085116161.html&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f68d1892\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/龍光地產及合景泰富合資以近170億投得鴨脷洲地皮-085116161.html</a><br />\n<br />\n地政總署公佈，鴨脷洲利南道地皮，由龍光地產及合景泰富地產，以168.6億元投得，高出市場上限近48%，是近4年來首幅百億地王。每呎樓面地價約22118元。<br />\n<br />\n市場原本對地皮估值介乎91.4億元至114.3億元，折合每呎樓面地價1.2萬元至1.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n地皮上週五截標，接獲14份標書。地皮面積近12.7萬平方呎，可建樓面面積約76.2萬平方呎，估計可提供約1420個單位。"},{"pid":"137189291cb2d4cb9cbac2d42bfb470720e0e207","tid":133554,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"錢多多都有<br />\n唔用邊有得洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地就錢換錢<br />\n惡果就香港人食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5a53493dc8b62bb638cd17fc5bc3856855ab32","tid":133554,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"合法漂白黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d14134141a7cb7e67ddb8be055a9bb0a13dcb2","tid":133554,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"其實無既，香港地主不嬲都係中國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f455b53a1035f68418b96949adccd110fb52ec",